videos.description: Matisse Thybulle gets the steal on one end setting up Noah Dickerson for the layup and-1.
videos.headline: Washington opens game with fast-break steal

videos.description: Arizona State's Mickey Mitchell is shoved to the ground by Washington's Michael Carter III while Nahziah Carter hangs on to his foot.
videos.headline: Players separated after tempers flare

videos.description: Matisse Thybulle pokes away the ball and passes ahead to David Crisp who makes the nice fast-break layup.
videos.headline: Washington's Crisp makes acrobatic layup after steal

videos.description: Washington and Arizona State trade baskets in the closing seconds of the 1st half, with De'Quon Lake slamming a huge putback dunk just before the buzzer.
videos.headline: ASU's Lake throws down massive putback dunk before halftime

videos.description: Shannon Evans II lobs up the alley-oop to De'Quon Lake who throws down the two-handed dunk.
videos.headline: Sun Devils connect on alley-oop dunk

videos.description: David Crisp drives to the basket and makes the acrobatic layup to avoid the defender.
videos.headline: Washington's Crisp makes acrobatic layup
